Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.40,0:01:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯母 杞纱呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.57,0:01:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 杞纱今天住在紫吴家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.84,0:01:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她说要和小透姊姊一起看动画录影带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.28,0:01:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱好像真的很喜欢小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.72,0:01:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人 真是难缠的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.55,0:01:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿里 你对我强大的力量也感到害怕了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.72,0:01:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我一旦回到家里也是怕老婆至上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.09,0:01:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怕老婆一族啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个敌人太不成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然会屈服在家庭的压力下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.90,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到敌人也有本难念的经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好难理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒觉得这部动画本身就有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 现在是晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.51,0:02:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你调整一下生活作息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.01,0:02:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为可以不必朝九晚五 我才选择当作家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你长得好像小纱喔 叔叔买点心给你吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.32,0:02:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是还没睡醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是今天想扮演恶质的父亲角色呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希今天也好冷漠喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点放开她 不然你身上的低劣细菌会传染给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 你们在看什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.27,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动画 大家都说有趣 在学校非常流行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就去借…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学校方面后来怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逐步地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.99,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心田乱舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鱼、小花 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去打工啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天见罗 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀 好像来得有点早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.77,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在更衣室里消磨时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一只鞋子掉下来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我捡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长得好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.79,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快帮我捡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.26,0:03:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.49,0:03:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛真的捡 蠢蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.76,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你没有一点自主性或是原则吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我叫你摔跤你也会摔跤吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你飞上天空你也会飞吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.37,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 毫无自我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 既然你捡了 就快点还给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你想偷走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有 我哪有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.88,0:03:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.45,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我特地来见你 你怎么一点礼貌都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.33,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会特地来找你这种人的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照你过去的经验 应该一下子就会想到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是草摩家的十二生肖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真迟钝 笨女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.17,0:04:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.14,0:04:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像没有传说中那么棒嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为是多惊人的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来也不过是一般标准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真傻 不该特地来找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少请我吃个饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欸!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欸什么咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不这样的话我不就吃亏了 快点答谢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.13,0:04:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我等一下还要打工 而且我身上没带多少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我看看你的皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这包包有点脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.57,0:04:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这本手册的颜色不错 我很喜欢深绿色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫草摩灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我想我们可能不会再见 还是把名字先告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.78,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你让我这么无聊 感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 那本手册里面有我妈妈的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈被抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.83,0:05:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得去跟他拿回来才行 现在也顾不得打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.01,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得碰到了新的十二生肖 我却没有时间感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.02,0:05:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在这里干嘛 感觉你好像迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈的照片啊 她妈妈还真时髦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看她只是个恋母情结的女生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你在这里干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要干嘛吗 我一定得做事不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.08,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你想说生产性低的人就不能活在这世上吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又没这样说 问你什么就答什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.68,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛 你问的问题我就都得回答吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我不想讲也得忍耐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个强词夺理的臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还背着小学生书包却这么的嚣张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛跟个小鬼认真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你丢到天空去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 手册…手册…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.40,0:06:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然追到这里来 你怎么知道我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你干了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 别胡乱猜好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一冤枉了别人 你要怎么跟人谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是拿了她的手册
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明明干了坏事 快点还给人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说这个什么话 是那个笨女人拜托我拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你别太嚣张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不想让嘴巴变形就快点把东西还她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.87,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你想被冠上凌虐儿童的罪就干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.27,0:07:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你拿了姊姊的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是杞纱 你好 你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 都是那只兔子唆使的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们问杞纱说你可能会去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你要还给她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.99,0:07:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能让姊姊难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神经病 我才不要这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.41,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.84,0:07:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么要对姊姊这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.98,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不希望你做出这种让她难过的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.52,0:07:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满嘴姊姊的 什么嘛 老是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是说那个笨女人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,录影带也一样 你一拿到就拿去她那里看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 是我借你的耶 你应该和我一起看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 灯路 你在借我录影带的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没兴趣 你喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借你吧 我没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本没跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道什么事都要说出来吗 你该自己察觉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你这样说太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别吵 死兔子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我没有任何力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.23,0:08:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你有事的时候我完全帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你满嘴只会讲姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我何尝不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.64,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的非常担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底发生什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你太迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.03,0:09:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路是在嫉妒小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.80,0:09:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然长得高 但灯路毕竟还是小学六年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然比较不会处理罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.44,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我一定和你一起看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之他把小透当情敌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高兴 不过好像太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透的立场也真难做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.29,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是得跟姊姊道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.90,0:09:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透今天本来要打工 现在都迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新遇到的这位十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常的聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.95,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还是很幼嫩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 就算你跟我道歉我也不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路必须受到惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊 你到底想干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"抱抱刑"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 这哪叫惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来你很喜欢灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.64,0:10:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次正式向你问候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.61,0:10:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 请多多指教罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.71,0:10:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有些不纯熟 却在谈一场可爱的恋爱的小男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.28,0:10:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我却是个怕老婆一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.42,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛 如果他不怕老婆就不会是反派吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是说对手不可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底这句台词有什么意义啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小灯 只不过是动画 不要太钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太甜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.31,0:10:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你该不是以为所有小孩都喜欢吃甜食吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你不知道这就是会蛀牙的原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的没想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讨厌 一点怜悯心都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.99,0:11:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系啦 杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然有关系 以后要注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.39,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我会注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.29,0:11:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可别搞错了 她不是你的佣人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到别人家里讲话还这么嚣张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛每次休假都跑来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛 这里什么时候开始变成猫咪当家啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.84,0:11:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底有什么贡献让我连句抱怨都不能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是说所有税金都是你在付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了那种什么责任也不负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却成天只会抱怨的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.62,0:11:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是提议问题 乳臭未干的小孩也会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.92,0:11:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.59,0:11:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路现在正值叛逆期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我管他什么叛不叛逆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要调情的话他不会回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.60,0:11:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是根本无法调情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是十二生肖的哪位 想要对女孩调情的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.67,0:12:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管在家里或外面都要有相当的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就别理他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.48,0:12:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你也跟他生气就表示你还是叛逆期喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.92,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 一说你就生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是好好锻链一下自己 变成像我这么出色的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连截稿日期都不遵守的人哪算是个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她站在我们大门口一副想要上吊的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么 为什么…为什么不准时交稿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师你这个浑蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.24,0:12:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会赶快写的 你今天还是先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 不能安静一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有 再给我倒杯茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都说过了 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上替你倒茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是 别什么都听他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个家真是越住越吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 不管这个小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.43,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你讨厌姊姊吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并不喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.13,0:13:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那为什么你要带我来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…因为你喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.61,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你来这里就会快乐 所以我才带你来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.55,0:13:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要待在姊姊旁边就会觉得很温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你们久等了 茶泡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去上厕所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.44,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 灯路他其实人很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.31,0:13:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们俩的感情真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.35,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直以为他讨厌我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.72,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是小学生时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.93,0:14:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们俩常在一起玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.46,0:14:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是突然间他变得好冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问他也不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我很震惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.11,0:14:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其实对你…很担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.49,0:14:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是男孩子的羞涩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.29,0:14:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许有其他理由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.76,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是十二生肖的每个人都有他们过去的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.77,0:14:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有着切不断的回忆或是浑沌的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.81,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些也缠绕在灯路那小小的身躯中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许他也有他的痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.82,0:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路他当时一定不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟慊人说出那句话会有什么后果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果慊人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人对于背着自己发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不会接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.14,0:15:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路就一直不敢接近杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而在这个期间 杞纱好像就被人欺负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.42,0:15:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他当然没办法保护她罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.02,0:15:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又没办法在她身边 这也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果因为自己而让自己心爱的人受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任谁都会胆怯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.44,0:15:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许不知道该如何发泄自己做的事的怒气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他就找小透出气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻就是这样不按牌理出牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 杞纱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今天不用打工吧 带我们去哪里玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们特地在下课后到这里来等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啦 特地来等你的 我们已经等很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再让我们站了 快点带我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…到底要去哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 这种事你自己也无法决定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道喜欢或讨厌你一点主见都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.84,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就想安稳地走在别人帮你安排的路上面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.91,0:16:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是活得太轻松了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.28,0:16:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里不是公园吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 你怎么选这么无聊的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你的脑子里没有输入电影院、游乐场这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.79,0:16:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我…我现在真的没钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜欢公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.03,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边有在卖可丽饼 你们要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱 你要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.71,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要巧克力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.97,0:17:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 杞纱你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要草莓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿不定主意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香蕉巧克力也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两种都很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.52,0:17:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们一人一半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.22,0:17:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 麻烦给我一个巧克力、一个草莓、一个香蕉巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吓…吓我一跳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杞纱的我来付 所以我的我也自己付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的你自己想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你站好吗 真难看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么连你这么笨的家伙都可以办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我就办不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你真的这么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.06,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管谁的什么烦恼你都可以帮他解决吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是什么样的痛苦或悲伤都能帮他消除？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以拯救他们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.97,0:18:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谦虚有时候反像是做作 拜托你别这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是她遇到和我相同困境时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许她能保护杞纱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想贯彻喜欢她的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是想让慊人了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.91,0:18:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢告诉杞纱 也不敢告诉慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只知道逃避 只会保持距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.62,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明知道她被欺负却什么也帮不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.12,0:19:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却还敢说自己喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.10,0:19:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么会这样？就因为我还是小孩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.57,0:19:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…明明什么都办不到 明明是个小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却去嫉妒突然出现的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在是太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么幼稚的自己 我真的是讨厌死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不应该是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不应该是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想变成个大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 我又没有要你了解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是说你这只是在拍马屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 你误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.61,0:20:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人不敢甚至避免去承认自己还很幼稚这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我妈妈告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.09,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以敢承认自己幼稚的人是个很有勇气的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你并不是什么都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.30,0:20:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会慢慢变成一个可以保护杞纱的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.17,0:20:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为在你的内心存在着勇气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.91,0:20:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你害怕 勇气还是会让你向前走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这话的意思是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.75,0:20:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我根本还不是个王子对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 你说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.49,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过你这段训话倒是值一个可丽饼 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天破例由我请客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不害羞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么王子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么证据也没有就在那边乱说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我将来无法变成王子 你会负责吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我无法变成王子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么让你高兴的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.66,0:21:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等着 我一定会变成王子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.03,0:21:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 就算死我也不会跟她道谢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灯路 找你的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.47,0:21:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我总不能一直靠灯路帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.54,0:21:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得提起勇气自己说出来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…这个礼拜天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是…你能一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.99,0:21:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我跟灯路一起玩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.86,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很乐意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.33,0:21:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 她真的是我的情敌

